Package edu.illinois.mitra.starl.modelinterfaces Description

Classes used to interact with real robots. This package contains all code related to sending instructions to real robots. Although different manufacturers expose different APIs to their robots, StarL makes an effort to wrap these APIs in a consistent manner, so that all aerial or ground robots may be controlled with the same interface. New models may be able to reuse an existing interface, or a new one may be required.
